rows.label: bf06140120_0020
rows.name:
Yes. I don't think anything less will
be sufficient to placate them.

rows.label: bf06140120_0030
rows.name: The Senate would never approve it...

rows.label: bf06140120_0040
rows.name: I can overrule them by decree.

rows.label: bf06140120_0050
rows.name:
Of course, I would need to secure
Senator Roderich's cooperation.

rows.label: bf06140120_0070
rows.name: If it's come to that... Well then I cannot dissent.

rows.label: bf06140120_0080
rows.name: I cannot help but admire your courage, Your Majesty.

rows.label: bf06140120_0090
rows.name: That means a lot, coming from you.

rows.label: bf06140120_0120
rows.name:
Is emergency, so Nilny take
liberty of drop by unannounced...

rows.label: bf06140120_0140
rows.name: So... What is this emergency you speak of?
